Project Setup
1️. Clone the Repository
git clone <your-repo-url>
cd culture-circle-outfit-recommender

Install Dependencies
Make sure Python 3.9+ is installed.
pip install fastapi uvicorn

Project Structure
.
├── main.py          # FastAPI entry point
├── data.py          # Product loading & normalization
├── rules.py         # Brand, color & occasion rules
├── scoring.py       # Scoring engine
├── products.json    # Product dataset (normalized)
└── README.md

Running the Application
Start the API server using Uvicorn:
- uvicorn main:app --reload

If the server starts correctly, you’ll see:
- Loaded XXX products
- Uvicorn running on http://127.0.0.1:8000 / uvicorn main:app --port 8001

Now crtl + Click om Url then write URL/docs 
Example: http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs

Nvigate to /products
Click on Try it Out
Here you can see all listings.

Navigate to /recommend/{product_id}
Click on Try it Out
Enter product_id 
Hit Execute button

Now in details you will se all recommendations with name, brand, etc.
At last you can See "match_score"
